lead_paragraph: Petra Kvitova's new year began with a withdrawal from the Shenzhen Open due to illness on Tuesday after losing the first set against China's Zheng Saisai.

headline.print_headline: Kvitova Withdraws From Shenzhen Open Due to Illness
